{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"19961-abrazos-en-la-ciudad","title":"Abrazos en la ciudad","description":"Abrazos de gatitos por la ciudad.","language":"Spanish","langCode":"es","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Ines Buresti"],"illustrators":["JP Brouard","Kalynne Vorster"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/19961-abrazos-en-la-ciudad"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29567/size3/3b99c56a34d0cfcfc37440bdd0610dd7.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29567/size6/3b99c56a34d0cfcfc37440bdd0610dd7.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29704/size6/0143049e7e2d83b1ecf5e3295e87dd01.jpg","text":"Mi nombre es Jilly.\nHoy, ¡he abrazado a casi todos los gatos de la ciudad!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29570/size6/9718063c5f55d085e9a5221913814082.jpg","text":"He abrazado a Ben, el gato de mi vecino. \n'Miau, miau', dijo Ben.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29573/size6/615037a38d80c4d3201d8f1c2d5f24ad.jpg","text":"He abrazado al gato que vive debajo del banco en la plaza.\nSe ha acurrucado y se ha meneado.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29574/size6/05584af56f8c06d4d1b81850f4c27869.jpg","text":"He abrazado al gato de la señorita Lilly. Un gato colorado y rechoncho.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29575/size6/ea5b90609a687a12b38282a66aa2a261.jpg","text":"Me ha lamido la cara.\n'Slurp, slurp, slurp.'","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29578/size6/4aeb4fc3879487db16df2609f049a47d.jpg","text":"También he abrazado al gato que vive fuera de la tienda de pescados.\n'Om, nom, nom', hizo el gato.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29582/size6/45bc58a13c2f2aad40040dc0b98246c2.jpg","text":"Hasta he ido a abrazar al gato gruñón, ¡que no le gustan los abrazos!\n                                No ha parado de gruñir.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29587/size6/8a68e302dc5258a97361f6349abfb1a0.jpg","text":"He abrazado a un gato largo.\n                                                      Y he abrazado a un gato bajo.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29585/size6/75e2a894ca2cdc815d490e8fad8cd1e3.jpg","text":"He abrazado a un gato viejo.\nHe abrazado a un gatito pequeño.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29586/size6/71b9ddab843d828c0f8e3684c2e26428.jpg","text":"He abrazado a un gato mamá,\ny a todos sus gatitos.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29588/size6/b90bf9999b741814ac8b58271718cbb2.jpg","text":"He tratado de abrazar a los gatos grandes del zoológico.\n-'¡NO!', me ha gritado el cuidador.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29589/size6/caa32c191ef19676e3cede3ad3ab596d.jpg","text":"Me he subido en el autobús y he abrazado a un gato que se escondía en el bolso de una señora.\n¡La señora chilló!","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29591/size6/b4c3c1ee8099be513fd607a8419d4cd4.jpg","text":"He vuelto a casa y me he metido en la cama. \nAlgo peludo se ha metido por debajo...","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29592/size6/d2e1f7905eaf67d9bba3c46945aec282.jpg","text":".... y me ha abrazado.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29593/size6/d4abf83fdbd4cb0ce6bb1b81d44c76aa.jpg","text":"16/16","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":15,"words":206}}